           	<td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white">
                      <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> <br />Hello again!<br /><br />Sorry to post another newbie question...I try to limit myself to no more than one dumb question in one day :)<br /><br />I thought that I had seen a merchant in Ak'Anon that sold a whole bunch of the initial research words that I will need (Words of the Sentient (Azia) and the like) to buy.  Could someone please remind me where this merchant is (or if I just made it up?).  I have been looking around, but I cannot seem to find him again.....I *THOUGHT* it was in that square room with the merchants in the four corners right outside the bank, but that doesn't appear to be the case.<br /><br />Any help/info would be appreciated.  Thanks again!<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Fastil<br />Lvl 14 GNecro <br />Lanys T'Vyl</span id="msg"></font>
