                      <img src="images/icon_mi_1.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="" title="" hspace="3" /><font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;10/14/2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 4:18:20 PM</font>
