                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> I've had great luck finding words on Bazaar/ShadowHaven vendors.  Also, traders often sell words for decent prices if you're missing one or two, but always check vendors first as they are generally much cheaper.<br /><br />As a side note, I found it to be much cheaper to just spend the plat to train research at my trainer over hunting down all the words for skillup combines.  Today for example I spent around 100pp gathering words from vendors/traders to get some skillups and ended up with only 2 skillups for my effort.  Each research skillup at trainer is currently costing me around 14pp and is just a click away :)<br /><br />Naenia - 40th Iksar Necro<br />Prexus Server</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
